customSql.expressionStatement:
SELECT 
    e."EMPLOYEEID", e."LASTNAME", e."FIRSTNAME", e."TITLE", 
    e."REGION", e."COUNTRY",
    t."TERRITORYDESCRIPTION", t."REGIONID",
    r.REGIONDESCRIPTION
FROM ${EMPLOYEE} e
LEFT JOIN ${EMPLOYEETERRITORY} et ON e."EMPLOYEEID" = et.EMPLOYEEID  
LEFT JOIN ${TERRITORY} t ON et."TERRITORYID" = t."TERRITORYID"
LEFT JOIN ${REGION} r ON t."TERRITORYID" = r."REGIONID"
